contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionarypar|ouzel|ousel}} '''Ouzel''' may refer to: *[[Common Blackbird]] or Ouzel, a species of thrush, all-black in the male *[[Lord Howe Island Thrush]] or Ouzel, an extinct subspecies of the Island Thrush *[[River Ouzel]], a river in England, a tributary of the Great Ouse ==See also== *[[Ring Ouzel]], a species of thrush *[[White-throated Dipper]] or Water Ouzel *[[American Dipper]] or Water Ouzel *''[[Ouzel Galley]]'', an Irish merchant ship *"''Iomramh an'' Ousel", a poem by [[Séamus Ó Néill]] *[[Woozle (disambiguation)]] {{disambig}}
